# DESCRIPTION
# Identify the conic and the orientation from its polar equation.
#
# ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Conic sections)
## Institution(John Wiley & sons)
## MO(1)
## TitleText1('Calculus')
## AuthorText1('Anton')
## EditionText1('9')
## Section1('10.6')
## Problem1('3')
